thread.title: Gloria Purse

author: Gloria Purse
title: Gloria Purse
text: Servcorp Deloitte - Parramatta have always provide us excellent professional services when required by a very lovely team of experienced, helpful and friendly staff. Ideally situated in Parramatta, close to public transport and Westfields Shopping. Every morning I am greeted with a friendly smile from Jaclyn, Jarnay & Sarah, which makes my day all that much better. Thanks Servcorp for making it right from the start of the day, it only gets better.
